                        "script": "\t\"\"\"\n\t\tWritten By: Aniket Sagar\n\t\tWritten Date: 14/11/2024\n\t\tPurpose: Add/Update values in db. \n\t\"\"\"\t\n\ttry:\n\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\u0027Lime8\u0027)\n\t\theader\u003dself.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntHeader\").getChild(\"lblHeader\").props.text\n\t\tisActive\u003dself.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntIsActive\").getChild(\"drpIsActive\").props.value\n\t\tmodelRange\u003dself.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntModelRange\").getChild(\"drpMode\").props.value\n\t\tareaName\u003dself.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntAreaName\").getChild(\"drpModel\").props.value\n\t\tareaName \u003d int(areaName[0])\n\t\tsystem.perspective.print(areaName)\n\t\tbomId\u003dself.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntCode\").getChild(\"drpCode\").props.value\n\t\tplant\u003dself.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntPlant\").getChild(\"drpMode\").props.value\n\t\tgearRatio\u003dself.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntGearRatio\").getChild(\"txt\").props.text\n\t\t#classificationId\u003dself.session.custom.classificationId\n\t\tcategory\u003d\u0027Classification Data\u0027\n\t\tsubCategory\u003d\u0027Classification Data Save Button\u0027\n\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\u0027Line 19\u0027)\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t#currentUserId\u003dself.session.custom.loggedInUserId\n\t\tcurrentUserId\u003d50\n\t\t\n\t\tif(self.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntHeader\").getChild(\"lblHeader\").props.text\u003d\u003d\"Add\"):\n\t\t\tId\u003d0\n\t\t\tparams \u003d {\"modelRange\":modelRange,\"areaName\":areaName,\"IsActive\":isActive,\"createdBy\":currentUserId,\"bomId\":bomId,\"Id\":Id,\"plant\":plant,\"gearRatio\":gearRatio}\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\"Params db add--------\u003e\")\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(params)\n\t\t\tqueryPath\u003d\"Project_VECV/Master/ClassificationData/insertUpdateData\"\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tdataset\u003dsystem.db.runNamedQuery(queryPath,params)\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\"After DB\")\n\t\t\tfor data in dataset:\n\t\t\t\tresult \u003d data[\u0027Result\u0027]\n\t\t\tif(result\u003d\u003d0):\n\t\t\t\tmessage \u003d str(bomId) +\" Configuration Already Exists!\"\n\t\t\t\tstate \u003d \"warning\"\n\t\t\telif(result\u003d\u003d1):\n\t\t\t\tmessage \u003d str(bomId) +\" Configuration details added successfully.\"\n\t\t\t\tstate \u003d \"success\"\n\t\t\t\t#auditMsg\u003dstr(code) +\" Configuration details added successfully.\"\n\t\telse:\n\t\t\tId\u003dself.session.custom.classificationId\n\t\t\t#Id\u003d50\n\t\t\tparams \u003d {\"modelRange\":modelRange,\"areaName\":areaName,\"IsActive\":isActive,\"createdBy\":currentUserId,\"bomId\":bomId,\"Id\":Id,\"plant\":plant,\"gearRatio\":gearRatio}\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\"params edit block-----------\u003e\")\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(params)\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tqueryPath\u003d\"Project_VECV/Master/ClassificationData/insertUpdateData\"\n\t\t\tdataset\u003dsystem.db.runNamedQuery(queryPath,params)\n\t\t\tfor data in dataset:\n\t\t\t\tresult \u003d data[\u0027Result\u0027]\n\t\t\tif(result\u003d\u003d0):\n\t\t\t\tmessage \u003d str(bomId) +\" Configuration Already Exists!\"\n\t\t\t\tstate \u003d \"warning\"\n\t\t\telif(result\u003d\u003d1):\n\t\t\t\tmessage \u003dstr(bomId) +\" Configuration details updated successfully.\"\n\t\t\t\tstate \u003d \"success\"\n\t\t\t\t#auditMsg\u003dstr(code) +\" Configuration details updated successfully.\"\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\tProject_VECV.PopUp.Alerts.showAlert(str(state), str(state.capitalize()), str(message), \"true\", \"Okay\", \"\", \"\", \"\", \"\", \"closePopup\", \"closePopup\", \"closePopup\",\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\")\t\n\t\t\n\t\tmessageType \u003d \u0027tableRefresh\u0027    \t \t\t\t\n\t\tsystem.perspective.sendMessage(messageType,payload\u003d{},scope \u003d \u0027page\u0027 )\n\t\t\n\t\tsystem.perspective.closeDock(\u0027rightp\u0027)\n\t\tsystem.perspective.openDock(\"rightView\")\n\t\tcreatedBy\u003dself.session.custom.loggedInUserId\n\t\t#Project_VECV.Configuration.Common.AddLogDetails.AddAuditLogs(category, subCategory, description, createdBy)\n\t\n\t\t\n\texcept:\n\t\tscreenName \u003d\u0027Classification Data Configuration for database\u0027   \n\t\tfilePath\u003dstr(\u0027Project_VECV/Pannel/Master/Classification Data Configuration\u0027)  \n\t\terrorFunction \u003d str(\u0027Event:onActionPerformed -\u003e cntSave/btn_Save\u0027)  \n\t\terrorType\u003dstr(\u0027Application\u0027)  \n\t\terrorCode \u003d str(Project_VECV.Common.GenerateUUID.getUniqueUUID())   \n\t\tdescription\u003dstr(sys.exc_info()[1]) #error description \n\t\tlineNumber\u003dstr(sys.exc_info()[2].tb_lineno) #lineno on which error \n\t\tProject_VECV.Configuration.Common.AddLogDetails.AddErrorLogs(screenName,filePath,errorFunction,errorType,errorCode,description,lineNumber) \n\t#End of except block\t"
                      },
